snippet.title: Shadow Legend VR | Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/987230/Shadow_Legend_VR/

Oculus Page: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/rift/2739977019349635

Shadow Legend is a full-length action-RPG exclusively made for VR. Releasing February 2019 for the HTC Vive & Oculus Rift, and soon after for the PlayStationVR.

Social Links:
